results.name: Triangle of the divisors of the coefficients of triangles A138771 and A165675
maple: nmax:=11: for n from 1 to nmax do a(n,1):=1 od: for n from 2 to nmax do for m from 2 to n do a(n,m):=(m-2)! od: od: for n from 1 to nmax do seq(a(n,m),m=1..n) od;
xref: A000012 (3x), A007395, A010722, A010863 equal the first six left hand columns.
A159333 equals, for n=>-1, all right hand columns.
